HEADWORD: chesty
<hw>chesty</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>marked by a large or
well-developed chest.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> big-chested.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>having or showing feelings of unwarranted importance
out of overbearing pride; <as>as, <ex>chesty</ex> as a
peacock</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> arrogant, self-important.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chetah</ent>⟦br⟧
